0:00:03.740,0:00:05.400
# 爆炒土鸡
"Baochao Tuji" ("Fiercely Stir-Fried Chicken")

0:00:05.400,0:00:08.000
# 首先我们准备黑皮土公鸡半只
First, prepare half a black-skin rooster

0:00:08.000,0:00:11.180
# 将土鸡剁成几大块之后再剁掉鸡屁股
Chop it into a few chunks, and chop off the butt

0:00:13.760,0:00:16.700
# 然后去掉指甲后将鸡肉剁成小块备用
Remove the claws, and then dice the chicken

0:00:16.825,0:00:20.145
# 同学们最好剁小块一些这样更容易爆炒和入味
Note: chop it into smaller dices, so that it's easier to cook and season

0:00:24.295,0:00:27.415
# 最后我们在处理鸡脖子的时候将鸡皮扯下来
Finally, when preparing the neck, tear off the skin

0:00:27.415,0:00:30.715
# 然后将吸附在鸡皮表面的淋巴清除干净
And remove all the lymphs there

0:00:30.720,0:00:33.920
# 鸡脖子上面的淋巴不分家养或者养殖都会有
Note that all kinds of chickens have lymphs at the neck

0:00:33.920,0:00:37.640
# 所以我们在处理鸡脖子的时候必须认真仔细检查一遍
So we must check carefully when processing the neck

0:00:46.580,0:00:49.500
# 最后将鸡头剁好之后准备辅料
Chop the head. Next, prepare the side ingredients

0:00:50.340,0:00:52.840
# 准备大蒜40克切成小粒备用
Dice 40g garlic for mise

0:00:52.840,0:00:56.720
# 同学们爆炒土鸡可以适量的多加一些大蒜这样更香
Note: for a baochao ("fierce stir fry ") dish, you may add extra garlic to make it more aromatic

0:00:58.935,0:01:01.935
# 准备几个二荆条去蒂之后切成小粒备用
Dice some "erjingtiao" chili peppers after removing the roots for mise

0:01:01.935,0:01:05.335
# 同学们也可以用魔芋或者小土豆代替二荆条
You may also use konjac or small potatoes as a replacement

0:01:07.380,0:01:09.840
# 准备小米辣40克切成小粒备用
Dice 40g "xiaomila" chili peppers for mise

0:01:09.840,0:01:11.900
# 不能吃辣的同学可以不加
Skip it if you can't handle spiciness

0:01:13.580,0:01:15.760
# 准备大葱2根切成小粒备用
Dice two green onions for mise

0:01:19.400,0:01:21.900
# 最后准备仔姜1小块切成小粒备用
Finally, dice a small piece of young ginger for mise

0:01:21.900,0:01:23.980
# 建议川外的同学加生姜更好
Regular raw ginger is more recommended for those outside Sichuan

0:01:23.980,0:01:26.040
# 因为出川后的仔姜味道会发苦
As young gingers outside Sichuan tend to be more bitter

0:01:26.040,0:01:29.660
# 温馨提示：此菜为家常小炒一锅成菜，无宽油
Kind reminder: this is a home cooking dish that cooks everything in one go; no "kuanyou" ("broad oil") is used

0:01:29.660,0:01:31.080
# 下一步开始制作
Next, cooking

0:01:31.085,0:01:33.365
# 首先我们在锅中加入适量的清水
First, add a moderate amount of water into the wok

0:01:33.365,0:01:35.545
# 然后将剁好的鸡头下锅焯水
Then parcook the chicken head

0:01:35.920,0:01:39.460
# 因为鸡头比较大块所以焯水之后更容易熟
As the chicken head is in bigger pieces, it's parcooked to ensure doneness

0:01:40.620,0:01:42.540
# 鸡头焯熟之后倒出备用
After parcooking, take out and drain the chicken head

0:01:43.440,0:01:45.160
# 然后我们把锅烧热
Next, heat up the wok

0:01:45.160,0:01:47.440
# 锅烧热之后再加入适量的熟菜籽油
And then add in a moderate amount of cooked rapeseed oil

0:01:50.180,0:01:51.920
# 将油温烧至6成热
Heat up the oil to 60%

0:01:53.155,0:01:55.815
# 油温6成热之后在锅中加入食用盐1勺（约3克）
And then add in a spoon of salt (~3g)

0:01:56.605,0:01:59.795
# 然后将剁好的鸡块下锅开中小火爆炒5分钟
Then add in the chicken dices, and stir fry over medium-low heat for 5 minutes

0:01:59.885,0:02:02.865
# 油中加盐的目的是让鸡肉更加的干香和入味
With salt in oil, the chicken can better dehydrate and absorb the flavors

0:02:10.740,0:02:14.560
# 当鸡肉炒至水份略干的时候再加入切好的大蒜和辣椒
With chicken slightly dehydrated, add in the diced garlic and chili peppers

0:02:16.160,0:02:19.020
# 料头下锅之后翻炒几下将大蒜炒香
Toss it evenly until aromatic

0:02:19.880,0:02:22.040
# 大蒜炒香之后加入老抽2克
Then add in 2g dark soy sauce

0:02:22.040,0:02:24.100
# 转小火将鸡肉翻炒上色
Turn to low heat and stir fry until colored

0:02:24.100,0:02:27.500
# 此菜不能加豆瓣酱所以加少许老抽上色
As doubanjiang is not good for this dish, we use dark soy sauce for coloring

0:02:27.500,0:02:31.440
# 鸡肉上色之后加入10克生抽酱油从锅边淋入炒香
Then add in 10g light soy sauce by drizzling at the edge of the wok, and stir fry until aromatic

0:02:35.920,0:02:38.840
# 最后再加入切好的大葱粒，仔姜粒，和辣椒粒
Finally, add in the diced onions, ginger and chilis

0:02:39.140,0:02:40.440
# 然后开始调味
Then we season the dish

0:02:40.440,0:02:43.300
# 锅中加入少许白糖中和辣味和提鲜
Add a little white sugar to neutralize the spiciness and enhance the umami

0:02:43.300,0:02:44.760
# 再加入少许胡椒粉
Also add a little ground white pepper

0:02:45.060,0:02:47.160
# 然后翻炒几下将辅料炒至断生
Then stir fry them till slightly cooked

0:02:48.755,0:02:52.055
# 最后再加入少许的晒醋从锅边淋入开大火翻炒均匀
Finally, drizzle in a little "shaicu" vinegar at the edge of the wok. Turn to high heat and toss it evenly

0:02:52.485,0:02:55.385
# 没有晒醋的同学可以用香醋或者陈醋代替
As a replacement, you may use other black vinegars like "xiangcu" or "chencu"

0:02:55.580,0:02:58.740
# 最后大火翻炒几下炒出锅汽即可出锅装盘
Stir fry over high heat until the "Guoqi" (aka "Wok Hei" or "breath of the wok") is realeased. Then it's ready to serve

0:03:02.720,0:03:05.060
