Next, technical summary

0:03:09.660,0:03:24.980
# 第一，鸡肉的品种的选择很重要，最好选择十个月以上的土公鸡
# 这样成菜有韧劲且不免
# 第二，食用盐先下锅的目的是让鸡肉在翻炒的时候入味至骨头
# 第三，生抽酱油和晒醋都必须翻炒出锅汽才香
1. It's very important to choose the right kind of chicken.
The best choice is naturally raised roosters of over 10 months old, which allows the right level of chewiness
2. By adding salt first, the chicken can be fully seasoned even to the bones
3. Light soy sauce and vinegar must be drizzled in at the edge of the wok and stir-fried till "Guoqi" is released

